            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Currently Cython doesn't support any Python versions below 3.8. Including in the Limited API.\n\nHowever - that was decided fairly late in the release process for Cython 3.1 and after I'd written the documentation for the Limited API. So unfortunately the documentation is wrong here.\n\nSorry about that. However the fix will be correcting the documentation rather than the Limited API.",
